column2: SELECT count(*) as &&&,   sum( case when (s.class=&&&) then # else # end) as &&&,  sum( case when (s.class=&&&) then # else # end) as &&&,  sum( case when (s.class=&&& and s.subclass=&&&) then # else # end) as &&&,   sum( case when (s.class=&&& and s.subclass!=&&&) then # else # end) as &&&  FROM WISE_xmatch as xm   JOIN PhotoObj AS p on xm.sdss_objid = p.objid  JOIN SpecObj AS s on p.objid = s.bestobjid  JOIN WISE_allsky AS w on xm.wise_cntr = w.cntr
